    "At the moment, it is up to the teacher or researcher to decide which type of formative feedback LEAP should provide.",
    "However, the importance of additional research cannot be overstated.",
    "Such research is essential to investigate whether a single type of formative feedback would yield equivalent benefits for all learners.",
    "It is rather likely that specific learner characteristics would influence the effectiveness of the feedback.",
    "Furthermore, empirical research is indispensable to verify the learning gains and the effectiveness of feedback provided by LLMs."
